4 motorized tension cables per rim section

Ring 2 — 500 Rim Sections
Second major ring

Also hosts biological + ecological + light‑industrial mods

Same mod size: 15m × 15m × 20m

4 motorized tension cables per rim section

Ring 3 — 2,000 Rim Sections (~0.95 g)
Final Gen‑1 ring

Outer rim gravity ≈ 0.95 g

Suitable for long‑term human habitation

4 motorized tension cables per rim section

